dct_title_s: Subdivision of property of James A. and Charles W. Jones in Brick Township, Ocean County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: This is a blueprint map of property along the Metedeconk River belonging to James A. and Charles W. Jones subdivided into housing lots and labelled with their respective owners.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Blueprint, Roy Theodore Havens, Engineer & Surveyor
